@Chapter{Retrieve RIRules with the feature (RIRule N-Regular)}@Label{ "Help-Browser 1" } @ItemClose the Browser Window (select it and press CTRL+W)@End-Item @ItemReopen it by clicking the @Application-Link{"browser button" | "German-Work.1-browser-button" } in the Document Window ofthe database German-Work.1 @End-Item @ItemChoose in the menu @Application-Link{ "Entity Restriction" |"German-Work.1-Browser-ENTITY-MENU"}, under the item 'Rules', thesub-item 'RIRules' @End-Item @ItemChoose in the menu @Application-Link{ "Feature Restrictions" |"German-Work.1-Browser-FEATURE-MENU" }, under the item 'RIRule', thesub-item 'N-Regular'@End-Item @ItemPress the @Application-Link{ "Retrieve button" |"German-Work.1-Browser-RETRIEVE-BUTTON" }@End-Item @ItemNow, the @Application-Link{ "central textfield" |"German-Work.1-Browser-CHOICE-TABLE" } lists all the RIRules with the feature(RIRule N-Regular) @End-Item 